### Crear orden con detalles (JSON)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ref": "ORD002",
  "idClient": 1001,
  "startDate": "2026-04-16 18:30:00",
  "description": "Primer pedido de prueba",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10",
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "phone": "600112233",
  "shopcartDetails": [
    {
      "bookId": 137,
      "amount": 2,
      "price": 29.99,
      "discount": 0.10
    },
    {
      "bookId": 138,
      "amount": 1,
      "price": 39.99,
      "discount": 0.05
    }
  ]
}

### Obtener orden por referencia
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD001
Accept: application/json

### Crear otra orden (con libro existente)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ref": "ORD002",
  "idClient": 1002,
  "startDate": "2026-04-16",
  "description": "Segunda orden",
  "address": "Avenida Central 20",
  "name": "Ana Garcia",
  "phone": "677889900",
  "paymentDate": null,
  "physicalData": null,
  "deliveryDate": null,
  "finishDate": null,
  "shopcartDetails": [
    {
      "bookId": 139,
      "amount": 3,
      "price": 25.50,
      "discount": 0.15
    }
  ]
}

### Actualizar orden existente
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/orders/ORD001
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ref": "ORD001",
  "idClient": 1001,
  "startDate": "2026-04-16",
  "description": "Pedido actualizado",
  "address": "Calle Mayor 10",
  "name": "Juan Perez",
  "phone": "600112233",
  "paymentDate": null,
  "physicalData": "Updated physical data",
  "deliveryDate": null,
  "finishDate": null,
  "shopcartDetails": [
    {
      "bookId": 137,
      "amount": 5,
      "price": 29.99,
      "discount": 0.20
    }
  ]
}
